.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: march, september, may, december
The people have 4 different hobbies: baking, collecting, dancing, gardening
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: adventure, comedy, fantasy, time-travel
1. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the far left##1
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the far left##1
3. the person who's birthday is in september is between the person who's birthday is in march and the person who's hobby is collecting##2
4. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
5. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the far right##1
6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
7. the person watching time-travel movies is the person who's hobby is gardening##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is the person who's birthday is in december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |   3    |    4    |
| Birthday          | may      | december | september | march |
| Hobby         | gardening   | collecting  | baking | dancing |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel | adventure   | comedy | fantasy |

