.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-12::.
There are 4 different favourite colors: ebony, apricot, pink, green
The people have 4 different hobbies: card-games, gardening, sudoku, traveling
4 different pets are kept: bird, goat, pony, turtle
1. the owner of the goat is on the right of the person who likes green##1
2. the person who's hobby is traveling is the person who likes pink##1
3. the person who likes apricot is between the person who likes pink and the person who's hobby is gardening##2
4. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the far left##1
5. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
6. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
7. the owner of the pony is on the right of the person who likes pink##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Color   | green | pink     | apricot | ebony       |
| Hobby      | sudoku  | traveling | card-games  | gardening |
| Pet        | turtle  | goat      | pony        | bird      |

