.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-15::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, adventure, epic, drama
The people have 4 different jobs:  paramedic, police-officer, project-manager, security-guard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, parkour, rugby, sailing
1. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person watching drama movies##1
3. the person watching documentary movies is the security-guard##1
4. the person watching epic movies is on the far left##1
5. the person who's sport is parkour is between the paramedic and the person watching documentary movies##2
6. the project-manager is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the person who's sport is biathlon is between the person who's sport is sailing and the person who's sport is parkour##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1     |        2        |       3        |       4        |
| Movie-Genre   | epic   | adventure           | documentary         | drama      |
| Job     | paramedic | project-manager | security-guard | police-officer |
| Sport   | rugby     | parkour         | biathlon       | sailing        |

