.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-16::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, iced-tea, mirinda, soy-milk
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: country, funk, rock, soul
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: golf, cricket, skateboarding, rowing
1. the fan of country is the person drinking iced-tea##1
2. the person drinking cola is between the person drinking mirinda and the person who's sport is cricket##2
3. the person drinking mirinda is the fan of funk##1
4. the person drinking mirinda is between the fan of rock and the person who's sport is rowing##2
5. the person drinking iced-tea is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
6. the person who's sport is golf is between the person who's sport is skateboarding and the fan of soul##2
7. the fan of country is the person who's sport is rowing##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |    4     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | mirinda | cola   | soy-milk |
| Music-Genre   | country  | funk    | rock   | soul     |
| Sport   | rowing  | skateboarding | golf | cricket   |

