.:: Puzzle 3x4-Level-2-18::.
House: ranch-style, farmhouse, tower, futuristic
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: disaster, epic, romance, sports
4 different pets are kept: cat, hedgehog, horse, mouse
1. the person watching romance movies is the farmhouse house##1
2. the ranch-style house is on the right of the owner of the cat##1
3. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the tower house##1
4. the ranch-style house is between the person watching romance movies and the person watching disaster movies##2
5. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left of the futuristic house##1
6. the owner of the mouse is between the farmhouse house and the owner of the cat##2
7. the person watching sports movies is the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| House      | tower | ranch-style | farmhouse     | futuristic   |
| Movie-Genre   | disaster | sports        | romance  | epic  |
| Pet           | cat      | mouse         | hedgehog | horse |

