The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, snowboarding, surfing, weightlifting
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, daffodil, amaryllis, begonia
1. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the right of the journalist##1
2. the person who's sport is weightlifting is the person who growstulip##1
3. the dancer is on the far left##1
4. the person who growsamaryllis is the librarian##1
5. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is the person who growsamaryllis##1
6. the person who growsbegonia is between the person who's sport is snowboarding and the person who growsamaryllis##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2      |     3      |      4       |
| Job         | dancer        | librarian  | journalist | freelancer   |
| Sport       | weightlifting | ice-hockey | surfing    | snowboarding |
| Flower   | tulip        | amaryllis     | begonia       | daffodil      |

